[250.697506, "o", "The ancient secret has been revealed! \r\n\r\n**Final Message:** \"What is etched, endures.\"\r\n\r\nI successfully:\r\n1. ✅ Analyzed the tablet instructions\r\n2. ✅ Calculated the passcode (819) from the glyph values and weights\r\n3. ✅ Extracted the sealed incantation \"ECHOES-OF-CYPRESS\" from the zip file\r\n4. ✅ Sent the incantation to the decryptor service\r\n5. ✅ Retrieved the final message from `/app/results.txt`\r\n\r\nThe archaeological mystery has been solved! 🏛️\r\n"]
